@node VERSION "Version and History"

- version 0.7 : creates a sequence of scripts for SPOTS. the moving
                of the points are only linear. all inputs are done
                in the shell.

- version 0.8 : the color-cycling of this points are implemented

- version 0.9 : little bug was eliminated

- version 1.0 : first full version, demo-version public

- version 1.1 : circles included

- version 2.0 : inputs are done in a window or on the screen.

@endnode
